OL,10,FToomaj Salehi, a 33-year-old Iranian
OL,11,Frapper, has been sentenced to death,
OL,12,Fas announced by his lawyer, Amir
OL,13,FRaessian, in an interview with
OL,14,FSharghdaily newspaper and .
