OL,5,Cspeak out
OL,7,FMr Salehi gained fame for his
OL,8,Foutspoken criticism of the Iranian
OL,9,Fregime in his music and his support
OL,10,Ffor the Woman, Life, Freedom movement,
OL,11,Fwhich started following the tragic
OL,12,Fdeath of while in police custody in
OL,13,FSeptember 2022.
OL,15,FSpeaking to ITV News, Mr Salehi's
OL,16,Fcousin, Azadeh Babadi, said: "He's
OL,17,Fvery strong. In a situation like this
OL,18,Fhe thinks of us, his family and his
OL,19,Ffans instead of being worried for
OL,20,Fhimself."
