OL,7,FResponding to Mr Salehi's thoughts on
OL,8,Fthe verdict, Ms Babadi replied: "I
OL,9,Fthink he would say it's okay. I know
OL,10,Fwhat I stand for, and I'm prepared to
OL,11,Fface whatever consequences come my way.
OL,13,F"Don't worry about me. I'll stand
OL,14,Fstrong until the very end.
OL,16,F"We have no hope with the Islamic
OL,17,FRepublic, but I beg the people outside
OL,18,Fof Iran to put pressure on their
OL,19,Fgovernments so maybe that way we can
OL,20,Fsave Toomaj with international
OL,21,Fpressure!"
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/6
