OL,7,FNegin Niknaam, a close friend and
OL,8,Fsocial media admin of Mr Salehi, told
OL,9,FITV News about reports of him facing
OL,10,Fthe death sentence: "It's baseless and
OL,11,Fsolely on grounds of his conversations
OL,12,Fwith fans and expressing his opinion
OL,13,Fin X and Instagram.
OL,15,F"He's being punished for speaking
OL,16,Fout," She continued.
