OL,3,C'We won't back down': Family of
OL,4,CIranian rapper facing death sentence
OL,5,Cspeak out
OL,7,F"Toomaj has always been the voice of
OL,8,Fthe voiceless in Iran through his
OL,9,Fmusic. His fans refer to him as the
OL,10,Fson of Iran, the lion of Iran.
OL,11,FFollowing the announcement of his
OL,12,Fdeath sentence, they were left shocked
OL,13,Fand are now demanding his release."
OL,15,FThe announcement of Mr Salehi's death
OL,16,Fsentence has sparked widespread
OL,17,Foutrage in Iran among his supporters
OL,18,Fas well as internationally.
