OL,7,FIn response, many people have wrote
OL,8,Fslogans and played his music as a form
OL,9,Fof protest.
OL,11,FThe rapper's family hope leaders
OL,12,Faround the world can continue to put
OL,13,Fpressure on Iran.
OL,15,FAuthorities in the country are yet to
OL,16,Fcomment on Mr Salehi's lawyers' claims.
